      "importance": 0.7,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "存储引擎选择 redb，因为它是纯 Rust 实现且 API 简洁",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.71,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为 Tantivy 支持中文分词，所以选它做全文检索",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.72,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "选择 DashScope 作为默认嵌入模型提供商",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.73,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "决定采用确定性提取器作为降级方案，不依赖外部 API",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.74,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "内存图结构选择邻接表表示，O(1) 出边查询",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.75,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "散列表使用开放定址而非拉链法，减少堆分配",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.76,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "决定用 SimHash 做语义签名，比 MinHash 更适合短文本",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.77,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "向量索引用 FlatIndex（暴力搜索），小规模时比 HNSW 更稳定",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.78,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "序列化选择 bincode 而非 JSON 或 protobuf，性能和体积最优",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.79,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为需要多通道召回，所以设计了 10 条召回通道",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.8,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "决定用 redb 的 Table 分区实现倒排索引",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.81,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "激活扩散的最大跳数设为 2 跳，平衡精度和延迟",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.82,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为要支持批量写入，所以设计了 write_batch API",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.83,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "consolidate 周期设为 1 小时，避免高峰时段资源争用",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.84,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "种子数设为每个通道最多 15 条，保证召回覆盖率",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.85,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
      "content": "用 energy-based 而非 score-based 做重排，更符合生物启发",
      "content_type": "Decision",
      "importance": 0.86,
      "group": "decisions"
    },
    {
